Wait for 3 seconds for the app to load

Wait for 3 seconds

Wait for 3 seconds
Verify the bottom navigation bar "My Account" is present

Suite/Test/Step Name: tap(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.widget.TextView - Vacation More. Get More"), 0)

Verify the text "Explore Westgate Loyalty" is visible

C667-Verify that the Term and Conditions in Guest Mode is displayed correctly
C668-Verify that the Privacy Policy in Guest Mode is displayed correctly
Launch the application on the physical device

Suite/Test/Step Name: tap(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.widget.TextView - Continue as a Guest"), 0)
Description: Tap on the clickable text "Continue as a Guest"
Wait for 10 seconds
Tap on the menu button
Wait for 30 seconds for the menu to open
Tap on the "Terms and Conditions" option in the menu

Suite/Test/Step Name: if (waitForElementPresent(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.view.View-Terms and conditions web"), 30, STOP_ON_FAILURE))
Description: Verify if the "Terms and Conditions" webview is present
Wait for 30 seconds
Tap on the cancel button to close the webview
Wait for 15 seconds
Tap on the menu button again to open the menu fly-out
Wait for 30 seconds for the menu to open
Tap on the "Privacy Policy" option in the menu
Verify if the "Privacy Policy" webview is present
Close the application successfully

C735-Verify that the Term and Conditions in Logged state is displayed correctly
C736-Verify that the Privacy Policy in Logged state is displayed correctly
Retrieve test data from "C739" data file
Extract the email and password from the test data
Launch the mobile application
Wait for 10 seconds to allow the app to load

Suite/Test/Step Name: tap(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.widget.Button - Login or Sign Up"), 0)
Description: Tap on the "Login or Sign Up" button to initiate login
Wait for 10 seconds before entering the email
Enter the email address in the login field
Wait for 10 seconds to allow input processing
Tap on the "Next" button to proceed to the password entry
Wait for 30 seconds
Enter the email again in the OAM (Online Account Management) login field
Hide the keyboard after entering the email
Wait for 30 seconds
Enter the password in the OAM password field
Hide the keyboard after entering the password
Wait for 30 seconds
Tap on the Login button in the OAM screen
Wait for 20 seconds to allow login processing
Navigate to the "Home" screen
Open the menu by tapping on the menu button

Description: Check if the "Terms and Conditions" menu option is present and tap it

Suite/Test/Step Name: if (waitForElementPresent(findTestObject("Object Repository/Repo/android.view.View-Terms and conditions web"), 10, CONTINUE_ON_FAILURE))

Tap on the "Cancel" button to close the webview
Open the menu again by tapping on the menu button
Tap on the "Privacy Policy" menu option
